---
<section style="padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-md); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
    
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">The <span class="text-accent glow-accent">Results.</span></h2>
    <p style="margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl) auto; max-width: 50ch;">Join our list of satisfied clients and see explosive growth with our absolute automation.</p>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: var(--space-2xl);">
      <div class="animate-fade-in delay-100">
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Client Savings</div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-6xl); color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1;">$5M+</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="animate-fade-in delay-300">
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Systems Created</div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-6xl); color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1;">100+</div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fade-in delay-500">
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Satisfaction Guarantee</div>
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-6xl); color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1;">100%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: calc(var(--space-2xl) * 1.2); display: flex; justify-content: center;">
      <a href="https://calendly.com/andrickjohn-l0n9/30min" target="_blank" class="btn" style="padding: 1.5rem 3rem; font-size: var(--text-lg);">
        Schedule Free Consultation
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
